      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YUNDERUP SUN (3) has a strong record this track and trip with 18 wins and 13 placings from 53 starts. In the money last time at this track (22.68) in a Grade 5, finishing a nose second. Has the ability and should feature. PRINCESS MILA (7) was well fancied last time on the strength of her recent form but could only manage third (22.92) at this track. Overdue and is among the main hopes. MR. TAYLOR (1) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw then burst clear to score (22.87) at this track in Mix 5 over 400m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. SEND IT KYE (8) hit the frame latest (17.45) when third at this track in a Grade 4. Has already won six times from this draw.",
